title: [Vornavian Coast, South Beach]
description: From high on top of the dunes, the beach stretches out to the north and south, endless sands dimly reflecting the soft rays of the moon.  Occasional dunes sport tall, sparse grasses on top, looking like the heads of so many balding men.

From high on top of the dunes, the beach stretches out to the north and south, endless sands reflecting the glaring rays of the sun.  Occasional dunes sport tall, sparse grasses on top, looking like the heads of so many balding men.
